<br>
There is a matter of grave concern with these recent adventuring bands which have set up. In these lost dungeons, you can gain items which you can combine with your existing items. However, you have to combine <br>
these items in a basin of water. <br>
<br>
This is unhygenic in the extreme. I know my brethren... the trolls and ogres (plus the occasional halfling or drunk dwarf). Most of them are not as educated, nay, even civilized, as myself. In short, to be blunt... the men are going to pee in these basins of water. <br>
<br>
So which you next go to augment an item.... look at the water in those basins. Closely. If its yellow, I would just back away. <br>
<br>
Venerable Haggatha Moles <br>
Troll Savage Lord <br>
